{"tid":842264,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"兩千元樓下電話相機拍攝效果,","createTime":"2018-09-30T07:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T04:42:36.000Z","uid":198097,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b76d688a99d653f02e3b22171a6f61945e5162f","tid":842264,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"SUGAR  S11  camera test for day &amp; night. 錄影測試, 歡迎意見.<br />\n港元兩千元樓下電話相機拍攝效果, 全方位Tested all four cameras<br />\n兩大缺點, 背部 16mp 鏡頭拍影片光暗黑白狂跳.偏暗, 暗位全死.<br />\n前置 20mp 鏡頭拍影片時轉向時跳格. 錯白平衡.<br />\n光拍照還是可以的. 拍影片死得. 尤其夜拍, 只能直站著定點拍攝.  鏡頭多，但也許是十年前的科技. 能接受嗎?, 心大心細又換機.<br />\n<br />\nRemark : This video has been edited by photos of windows, (把黑暗的部分放亮, 但是失去了解析度)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuNePc5F6Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZuNePc5F6Ew&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflUzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=cef8696b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuNePc5F6Ew</a><br />\n<br />\n手機cam的重要性,<br />\n1) 普通人不會經常帶單反雙反 camera 出街.<br />\n2) 2019, 2020, 任何時候你都可以買更新的手機. 無論是硬件還是軟件.<br />\n3) 但你永遠不能夠回到2018年再拍攝錄影."},{"pid":"3be4c307f0d884270357d5b34acff022601f404f","tid":842264,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"在與SUGAR商討後，他們同意重新檢查手機甚至更換鏡頭."},{"pid":"3f8dae6485939ff407430b93f62382685b9cf56e","tid":842264,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10be9a555aabf56746cc8656d25f31cf64c10a1e","tid":842264,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3f8dae6485939ff407430b93f62382685b9cf56e","tid":842264,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"得罪你嗎?"},{"pid":"fbce23f5f70c3d85c82e5aa2ef214b795b225223","tid":842264,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c